HEADWORD: Commentate
<hw>Com"men*tate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t. & i.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>commentatus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>commentari</ets> to
meditate.]</ety> <def>To write comments or notes upon; to make
comments.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Commentate</qex> upon it, and return it enriched.</q>
<rj><qau>Lamb.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

